<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">
  <PropertyGroup>
    <Title>iSukces.Cli.Punctuate</Title>
    <Description>.NET process wrapper for restoring punctuation and sentence boundaries by invoking a Python punctuation script as a separate operating-system process. The package prepares command-line arguments, exchanges input/output through temporary files, and optionally exposes helpers that can start user-side external tools such as uv or pip; it does not include, redistribute, or license Python, PyTorch, Hugging Face Transformers, SentencePiece, or the kredor/punctuate-all model.</Description>
